But yeah, I would say,
what I went through

740
00:48:06,070 --> 00:48:08,610
is going to be
foundational for the final.

741
00:48:08,610 --> 00:48:13,510
So I guess if you understood
everything I said,

742
00:48:13,510 --> 00:48:16,370
I think you're going to
be ready for the final.

743
00:48:16,370 --> 00:48:18,395
So, yeah.

744
00:48:18,395 --> 00:48:20,270
But if you have any
questions, Shervine and I

745
00:48:20,270 --> 00:48:22,910
are always here to--

746
00:48:22,910 --> 00:48:23,410
oh, yeah.

747
00:48:23,410 --> 00:48:24,243
You have a question.

748
00:48:29,190 --> 00:48:32,870
Yes, so the question is the
scope for the final lecture

749
00:48:32,870 --> 00:48:33,770
5 to lecture 8.

750
00:48:33,770 --> 00:48:35,070
Yes.

751
00:48:35,070 --> 00:48:38,150
So for midterm, it was
