1502
01:36:26,220 --> 01:36:30,300
So I think it reflects the fact
that you need to be smarter

1503
01:36:30,300 --> 01:36:34,900
in the compute that you spend
for serving LLM queries at test

1504
01:36:34,900 --> 01:36:35,700
time.

1505
01:36:35,700 --> 01:36:39,780
And I think this will
motivate more and more

1506
01:36:39,780 --> 01:36:44,820
this line of research
in the coming years.

1507
01:36:44,820 --> 01:36:47,860
And then there is another
area that we've not

1508
01:36:47,860 --> 01:36:51,700
